rComments: She is all around an amazing person! She is young, fun and vibrant. She keeps all the students engaged. While she has a fun side, she is serious about academia; she will go through tough walls to engage all students and make sure everyone is learning and understands the same material taught.

Group projects are easy to do and read for. Taking the quizzes are the harder part. Because the information is general, your answers could apply, but if the group doesn't put that response on their answer key then its wrong. Doc does reviews before the quiz. Be aware that she loves to talk and catch up. She is chill but intelligent.
